Bleecker Street, north side, east from Jones to Cornelia Streets. The 4 story building to the left is No. 275 Bleecker Street, a frame structure that adjoins the tenement at the N. E. corner of Jones Street. View 3 shows this solely and is photographed from Morton St. Note in the latter views, the Italian pushcart market that has sprung up here.

J. J. Corell
P. L. Sperr Collection

J. Clarence Davies Collection
Museum of the City of N. Y.
